title: Ep. 633 Justice is Coming for the Swamp Rats
description:
What actually happens during a government shutdown?

Read this terrific piece which points out some of the troubling connections between Fusion GPS, the Russians, the Clintons, and the Obama administration.

Finally, some justice in the Uranium One scandal.

Yes, Uranium was exported out of the United States. Liberals are lying about this inconvenient fact. Read this piece for clarification.

If the UK wasn’t supplying intelligence on Trump to the Obama administration then why did CNN report on it? Read this piece.

What did the NSA get in return for millions in support to the GCHQ?

Why did the head of the GCHQ resign unexpectedly?
